            "content": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"docs/demo.svg\" alt=\"Orion Status — Artemis II Tracker\" width=\"800\"/>\n</p>\n\n<h1 align=\"center\">orion-status</h1>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  Real-time Artemis II Orion spacecraft tracker for your terminal.<br/>\n  Live telemetry from NASA Deep Space Network + JPL Horizons, rendered as a status line or full TUI.\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/orion-status\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/npm/v/orion-status?color=e3b341&label=npm\" alt=\"npm\"/></a>\n  <a href=\"#data-sources\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/data-NASA%20DSN%20%2B%20JPL-58a6ff\" alt=\"data sources\"/></a>\n  <a href=\"#license\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-3fb950\" alt=\"license\"/></a>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n## Install\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g orion-status\n```\n\nOr run directly:\n\n```bash\nnpx orion-status\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n### Claude Code status line\n\nAdd to `~/.claude/settings.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"statusLine\": {\n    \"type\": \"command\",\n    \"command\": \"echo '{\\\"unused\\\":true}' | npx orion-status\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Standalone TUI\n\n```bash\norion-status --tui\n```\n\nFull-screen dashboard with animated Orion sprite, trajectory bar, crew roster, and live milestone countdown.\n\n## Data sources\n\nLive telemetry from two sources, merged on a Cloudflare Worker:\n\n| Source | Interval | What |\n|---|---|---|\n| **NASA Deep Space Network** | 5s | Ground station range (Goldstone/Madrid/Canberra) |\n| **JPL Horizons API** | 1min | Full state vectors for Orion (`-1024`) and Moon (`301`) |\n\nClient interpolates between data points using velocity so the km counter ticks every render frame.\n\nFallback chain: CF Worker &rarr; direct Horizons &rarr; local cache &rarr; placeholder.\n\n## Mission milestones\n\n22 events from JPL trajectory data with countdown precision to seconds:\n\n| Event | MET |\n|---|---|\n| TLI burn | T+25h 8m |\n| Closest lunar approach | T+120h 31m |\n| Manual piloting demo | T+172h 20m |\n| Entry interface Mach 32 | T+217h 29m |\n| Splashdown | T+217h 42m |\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nNASA DSN XML ──> CF Durable Object (5s alarm) ──> KV ──> GET /position\nJPL Horizons  ──> CF Cron (5min)               ──> KV ──/\n                                                        |\n                                              Client (interpolation)\n                                                        |\n                                              Terminal status line\n```\n\n## Development\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run build\nnpm test        # 18 tests\n```\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n",
